author: Xherus
title: Good Keychain but not Proportioned to a 2x4 Brick
review:
Globally a great keychain for an okay price in VIP points.

  • The proportion is NOT accurate to a 2x4 brick. It's larger and flat. Surprising at first but better for a pocket. I like it that way.
  • The metal finish is excellent.
  • The quality of the box is great and a nice bonus.
